title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 7 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 7 2022
description:
Video emerges of Draymond Green of the Golden State Warriors punching out teammate Jordan Poole at practice. NBA punishes words, but not violence. Buck's weekend reading plans. Fox and CNN cover Biden economic speech very differently. Caller on violence in New York. Kanye West talks to Tucker Carlson. Florida Governor Ron DeSantis joins Clay and Buck to provide an update on the Hurricane Ian recovery, which, under DeSantis' leadership, Joe Biden had called "remarkable."

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
